      • ProcessStationResAbstrAnimation

        public ProcessStationResAbstrAnimation(ModelAnimation owner,
                                       java.lang.String name,
                                       java.lang.String resName,
                                       int resTotal,
                                       Position pos,
                                       FormExt form,
                                       ListInterface list,
                                       boolean showInAnimation)
        Build a ProcessStation. This Station contains some process entries. Each Entry contains some animated process entities. For each entry, the no of used resources are shown. With insert a new process entry is created and with remove a process entry will be deleted. A process entry looks like a working station.
        Parameters:
        owner - used model
        name - name of process-station
        resName - name of resource (for information only)
        resTotal - total nr of available resources
        pos - middle point of animation object
        form - form of animation object
        list - queue from where process-entities are coming, maybe null
        showInAnimation - switch animation on or off
